chat_poem:
In a WhatsApp group so bright and new,
Where minds like lions, brave and true,
Built an AI system, scaling high,
While Solana dreams touched the sky!

Shabs created, crowned with care,
A space where brilliance filled the air,
With NDAs and protocols tight,
Innovation blooming day and night!

Four-thirty calls we'd coordinate,
Across time zones we'd navigate,
Building futures, bit by bit,
With hackathon spirit and tech-savvy wit!

Our brainstorms sparked like holiday lights,
Taking projects to spectacular heights,
Together we'll scale a hundred fold,
Creating wonders that will soon unfold!
